## Rules of engagement

- Never bypass the constitution — amendments go through the PR + ADR path in
  the constitution's amendment section.
- Never edit `platform-manifest.json` by hand.
- Never create a new skill file directly in `.agent/skills/`; skills ship via
  platform modules. Project-local prompts and scripts belong under
  `.agent/prompts/` or `.agent/scripts/`.
- Always cite your sources: constitution clauses, spec requirement IDs, lore.
- Do NOT overlay onto source directories (`src/`, `app/`, `backend/`,
  `frontend/`, `lib/`); that is a property of the overlay itself. If you find
  the overlay has touched a source path, stop and file an issue against the
  platform.

